OL,3,CCounty lines drugs gangs operating out
OL,4,Cof caravan holiday parks
OL,6,FCaravan parks in Lincolnshire are
OL,7,Fbeing used by gangs to distribute
OL,8,Fdrugs, according to one site owner.
OL,10,FJen Limb, who runs Littlehaven Park at
OL,11,FChapel St Leonards between Skegness
OL,12,Fand Mablethorpe, said holiday sites
OL,13,Fexperience extra problems with crime
OL,14,Fas visitor numbers swell during the
OL,15,Fsummer.
