OL,3,CCounty lines drugs gangs operating out
OL,4,Cof caravan holiday parks
OL,6,FShe said: "You get caravan thefts.
OL,7,FWe've also noticed across the coast an
OL,8,Fincrease in domestic violence and,
OL,9,Fmore seriously, people are using
OL,10,Fcaravans as a way of hiding county
OL,11,Flines.
OL,13,F"They're using vulnerable people or
OL,14,Fchildren, installing them in caravan
OL,15,Fparks because it's quite anonymous and
OL,16,Fthen using them to distribute drugs."
