OL,3,CCounty lines drugs gangs operating out
OL,4,Cof caravan holiday parks
OL,6,FCounty lines is the term used to
OL,7,Fdescribe the practice of dealers
OL,8,Ftransporting drugs from one area to
OL,9,Fanother, often across police and local
OL,10,Fauthority boundaries and from larger
OL,11,Ftowns and cities to more rural areas.
OL,13,FGangs usually recruit children or
OL,14,Fvulnerable people to ferry the drugs.
OL,15,FThe "county line" is the mobile phone
OL,16,Fline used to take the orders of drugs.
OL,18,FLincolnshire's coast has more than 260
OL,19,Fcaravan sites with around 36,000 units.
