OL,3,CCounty lines drugs gangs operating out
OL,4,Cof caravan holiday parks
OL,6,FSkegness alone sees its population
OL,7,Fswell from 20,000 to around 250,000 in
OL,8,Fthe height of summer.
OL,10,FThe county's police force has
OL,11,Fdeveloped specific plans designed to
OL,12,Fcombat crime during the summer,
OL,13,Fincluding a Caravan Watch scheme,
OL,14,Fsimilar to Neighbourhood Watch.
OL,16,FBut Ms Limb said a decision last year
OL,17,Fto halve the number of police
OL,18,Fcommunity support officers (PCSOs)
OL,19,Femployed by Lincolnshire Police was
OL,20,Fthe wrong one.
