OL,6,F"(PCSOs) really helped with crime
OL,7,Fprevention and dealing with crimes as
OL,8,Fand when they happen," she said.
OL,10,FLincolnshire Police said it
OL,11,F"acknowledged the use of caravans in
OL,12,Fcounty line drug dealing".
OL,14,FBut Det Insp Daniel McCormack said:
OL,15,F"It is not something that is regularly
OL,16,Fseen and should not put people off
OL,17,Fcoming to Lincolnshire to enjoy
OL,18,Fthemselves.
