OL,3,CCounty lines drugs gangs operating out
OL,4,Cof caravan holiday parks
OL,6,F"We have recently disrupted a county
OL,7,Fline drug gang operating out of a
OL,8,Fcaravan on the east coast, resulting
OL,9,Fin the seizure of drugs and cash.
OL,11,F"This has led to a successful
OL,12,Fprosecution of offenders. We are
OL,13,Fcontinually reviewing intelligence
OL,14,Faround drug activity and take robust
OL,15,Faction where necessary.
