OL,6,F"It is well-known that criminals will
OL,7,Fregularly seek opportunities to hide
OL,8,Fand deal drugs in accommodation
OL,9,Fnationally, and that business model
OL,10,Foften targets rural and coastal
OL,11,Fcommunities."
OL,13,FHe said there were "good relations"
OL,14,Fwith Caravan Watch and efforts
OL,15,Fcontinued to educate the tourist
OL,16,Findustry about the signs of county
OL,17,Flines dealing.
